{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Origin","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Origin","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Web 内容的源由用于访问它的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/URL\">URL</a> 的方案 (协议)，主机 (域名) 和端口定义。只有当方案，主机和端口都匹配时，两个对象具有相同的起源。</p>\n<p>某些操作仅限于同源内容，而可以使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/CORS\">CORS</a> 解除这个限制。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"同源的例子","title":"同源的例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>same origin because same scheme (<code>http</code>) and host (<code>example.com</code>)</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>http://example.com/app1/index.html</code></li>\n  <li><code>http://example.com/app2/index.html</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>same origin because a server delivers HTTP content through port 80 by default</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>http://Example.com:80</code></li>\n  <li><code>http://example.com</code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"不同源的例子","title":"不同源的例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>different schemes</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>http://example.com/app1</code></li>\n  <li><code>https://example.com/app2</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>different hosts</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>http://example.com</code></li>\n  <li><code>http://www.example.com</code></li>\n  <li><code>http://myapp.example.com</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>different ports</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>http://example.com</code></li>\n  <li><code>http://example.com:8080</code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":"<p>详细信息，请看<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Security/Same-origin_policy\">同源策略</a>。</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"同源的例子","id":"同源的例子"},{"text":"不同源的例子","id":"不同源的例子"},{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"Web 内容的源由用于访问它的URL 的方案 (协议)，主机 (域名) 和端口定义。只有当方案，主机和端口都匹配时，两个对象具有相同的起源。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Origin","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Origine","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Origin (オリジン)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"출처","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Origem","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Первичные данные","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/origin","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/origin/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Origin","title":"Origin"}],"pageTitle":"Origin - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}